<p rend="no-indent">My dear Papa</p>
<lb/><p><space extent="8" unit="chars"/>I have given a month's
<lb/>notice to <persName>Mr Handford</persName> to leave
<lb/>the work of the school entirely.
<lb/>It must by<hi rend="underline"> no means</hi> lead you
<lb/>to think that I dislike it <w>al<supplied><seg type="hyphen">-</seg></supplied>
<lb break="no"/>to-gether</w>; but I am delighted in this
<lb/>great work I have been working
<lb/>as you know here and in <unclear cert="medium"><settlement>Rabai</settlement></unclear>
<lb/>without showing any sign of <w>disa<supplied><seg type="hyphen">-</seg></supplied>
<lb break="no"/>tisfaction</w> and <add place="below"><seg type="metamark">^</seg></add> <add place="above">now</add> what makes me to have
<lb/>some dislike of it? It is not the 
<lb/>work itself but <hi rend="underline">freedom in teaching</hi>
<lb/>I wish that it were given to me
<lb/>to undertake another <w>bra<add place="below"><seg type="metamark">^</seg></add><add place="above">n</add>ch</w> of
<lb/>the same work; that is to make

<pb facs="liv_020052_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/><hi rend="underline">an infant school</hi> in another
<lb/>place, (it may be sure that there
<lb/>are more slaves to come), it should
<lb/>be under my own guidance.
<lb/>I know at present there is 
<lb/>danger for me in getting no
<lb/>work, as there are plenty to 
<lb/>do here.</p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="3" unit="words"/>I remain yours
<lb/><space extent="4" unit="words"/>failthfully
<lb/><space extent="3" unit="words"/><hi rend="underline"><persName>J. Wainwright</persName></hi></p>
<lb/>
